,"uid":356914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:34:25.000Z","msg":"牙Q"},{"pid":"8ac606881f71170b72adf13bbe61614fbabf1ecc","tid":2025610,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"投降啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f2bfbba4907151c30bf9ddd407ee134d116167","tid":2025610,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"成個鐘都未有金剛棒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f226d0f1570a2b72b7dc836040aff83eb9a685b","tid":2025610,"uid":343356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12ebc65f76ead30de7d4f1eb30164f55bd6ec117","tid":2025610,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:01:51.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧向台灣總統蔡英文發出賀電，中國官媒《環球時報》發表社評，指「中國正在變得越來越有力量，我們對台灣宣示主權的能力肯定也是越來越強的」，並說「現在可不是1996年『台海危機』的時候了，大陸的軍事力量已經能夠有效震懾台軍，威懾美軍」，但就說「北京無需對蓬佩奧電賀蔡英文開啟第二任期直接激烈反應」。<br />\n<br />\n《環球時報》在社評〈美台想開啟新遊戲？大陸可是最玩得起〉說，蓬佩奧這樣做，「明擺着是給北京看的。是的，我們看到了美國政府正在台灣問題上開倒車，用『切香腸』的方式試圖消磨北京在這個問題上的底線，同時有意刺激大陸方面，當成與北京博弈的牌一張一張往外甩」。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該報稱，「北京無需對蓬佩奧電賀蔡英文開啟第二任期直接激烈反應，但我們需要給他們記一筆賬。他們的這種小動作多了，就單給他們列一個黑賬本」，又說「大陸方面很清醒，我們一方面不會被華盛頓的這些動作帶偏了節奏，一方面會做出新的台海博弈安排，牢牢把握這一地區局勢的戰略主動權，最終粉碎美台的所有圖謀」。<br />\n<br />\n社評最後說，「如果美軍更多來這個地區攪和，最受傷害的首先是台灣經濟，美國的戰略風險一點也不比中國大陸的小。那將是中國大陸非常玩得起的『長期遊戲』」，「他們需要猜一猜，如果大陸說『你搞你的，我搞我的』意味着什麽，以及他們會在什麽時候從哪個方向挨一棍子」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/30063/蔡英文就職典禮-蓬佩奧-環球時報-30063/蓬佩奧\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F30063%2F%E8%94%A1%E8%8B%B1%E6%96%87%E5%B0%B1%E8%81%B7%E5%85%B8%E7%A6%AE-%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7-%E7%92%B0%E7%90%83%E6%99%82%E5%A0%B1-30063%2F%E8%93%AC%E4%BD%A9%E5%A5%A7&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krPrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=ca95fe75\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/30063/蔡英文就職典禮-蓬佩奧-環球時報-30063/蓬佩奧</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"哦 咁唔好打仗啊 直接承認台灣獨立啦😂😂😂"},{"pid":"4bd32185c33e078fd93387333748dd78cd75c593","tid":2025610,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8b5ed625b3c6e929318aa3b0ad6ac1f20a2b53c","tid":2025610,"uid":153679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"無需激烈反應 但要記帳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65658978e58c000127ffa7600849240f5b99962","tid":2025610,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:55:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ced76cbc6a785cbfa8b6c814ab6f85956403ae","tid":2025610,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傻閪"},{"pid":"234823e0a9120c5ac613142db13a4e045c1f74fa","tid":2025610,"uid":70840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"留左comment叫班大陸狗武統台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠膽就打 唔好口交啦屌"},{"pid":"68718e37ef095bda0b8b3bebcdd1e6e4954cae15","tid":2025610,"uid":2360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime